These files can be used with debconf to create a Debian package.

A more up to date version of these files may be available at
https://github.com/christiscarborough/gmrender-resurrect-debian

Contributed by Christi Scarborough <christi@coraline.org>.

---
There is an additional service file gmediarender.service.
When copied to /lib/systemd/user/gmediarender.service
any user can start gmediarender interacting with the pulseaudio/pipewire user session with

```
systemctl --user enable gmediarender
systemctl --user start gmediarender
```

